OP_RETURN

### Locktime
OP_CHECKLOCKTIMEVERIFY
OP_CHECKSEQUENCEVERIFY

### Crypto
OP_RIPEMD160
OP_SHA256
OP_HASH160
OP_HASH256
OP_CHECKSIG
OP_CHECKSIGVERIFY
OP_CHECKMULTISIG
OP_CHECKMULTISIGVERIFY

